e constitution of meaning in spoken language.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 17. Dez 2021) 0aGerman languagexGrammarvCongresses. 7aLANGUAGE ARTS & DISCIPLINES / Linguistics / General.2bisacsh1 aEisenberg, Peter, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aFiehler, Reinhard, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aGohl, Christine, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aGünthner, Susanne, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aHegedüs, Ildikó, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aHennig, Mathilde, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aHennig, Mathilde, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aImo, Wolfgang, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aKappel, Péter, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aSelting, Margret, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aStoltenburg, Benjamin, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aÁgel, Vilmos, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aÁgel, Vilmos, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDGBA Linguistics and Semiotics 2000 - 2014z9783110636970oZDB-23-DLS08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertE-BOOK GESAMTPAKET / COMPLETE PACKAGE 2006z9783110277128oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertE-BOOK PAKET LINGUISTIK UND LITERATURWISSENSCHAFT  2006z9783110276893oZDB-23-DGA0 cprintz978348431269240uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978311093606340uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783110936063423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783110936063/original  aEBA